text: Toomas Tiru (born 18 January 1969) is an Estonian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Estonian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Estonia Category:Estonian male biathletes Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Viljandi
